  ('05df7cf9-a15a-4dc7-b27c-268a266f1af7-ex1', '05df7cf9-a15a-4dc7-b27c-268a266f1af7', 'bored', 'The kids got bored on the long trip.', '长途旅行让孩子们感到无聊。'),
