  ('2fda486b-06cf-4599-98c8-78af4be30641-ex2', '2fda486b-06cf-4599-98c8-78af4be30641', 'glimpse', 'The disclosures offer a rare glimpse into the agency''s internal deliberations.', '这些披露为窥见该机构的内部讨论提供了难得的机会。'),
