  ('f1492234-3904-45e3-b413-fa1f73eda580-ex1', 'f1492234-3904-45e3-b413-fa1f73eda580', 'harmony', 'The choir sang in perfect harmony.', '合唱团的和声完美无瑕。'),
  ('f1492234-3904-45e3-b413-fa1f73eda580-ex2', 'f1492234-3904-45e3-b413-fa1f73eda580', 'harmony', 'The directive seeks harmony among previously divergent national standards.', '该指令力求统一此前各不相同的国家标准。'),
  ('49516775-c2da-4a58-9392-810621c51f97-ex1', '49516775-c2da-4a58-9392-810621c51f97', 'solely', 'The decision rests solely with you.', '决定权完全在你。'),
  ('49516775-c2da-4a58-9392-810621c51f97-ex2', '49516775-c2da-4a58-9392-810621c51f97', 'solely', 'The entities existed solely to obscure the beneficial ownership.', '这些实体存在的唯一目的就是掩盖受益所有权。'),
  ('f3242e58-7ef1-49a6-acfe-d7a2b9fafe78-ex1', 'f3242e58-7ef1-49a6-acfe-d7a2b9fafe78', 'deficiency', 'The doctor found a vitamin deficiency.', '医生发现了维生素缺乏症。'),
  ('f3242e58-7ef1-49a6-acfe-d7a2b9fafe78-ex2', 'f3242e58-7ef1-49a6-acfe-d7a2b9fafe78', 'deficiency', 'The audit identified deficiencies that successive reviews had normalized.', '审计发现了被历次审查习以为常的缺陷。'),
  ('553fbaff-15cc-4694-9059-843aab242060-ex1', '553fbaff-15cc-4694-9059-843aab242060', 'definite', 'We need a definite answer by Friday.', '我们周五前需要明确的答复。'),
  ('553fbaff-15cc-4694-9059-843aab242060-ex2', '553fbaff-15cc-4694-9059-843aab242060', 'definite', 'The offer lapses absent definite acceptance within the prescribed period.', '如未在规定期限内明确承诺，该要约即告失效。'),
  ('d001be7b-08cd-4e9d-9160-77e36c398cab-ex1', 'd001be7b-08cd-4e9d-9160-77e36c398cab', 'tolerance', 'The school has zero tolerance for bullying.', '学校对霸凌零容忍。'),
  ('d001be7b-08cd-4e9d-9160-77e36c398cab-ex2', 'd001be7b-08cd-4e9d-9160-77e36c398cab', 'tolerance', 'The specifications permit deviation only within prescribed tolerances.', '技术规格仅允许在规定公差范围内的偏差。'),
  ('50627e13-92e9-4af3-b070-db654649f5f0-ex1', '50627e13-92e9-4af3-b070-db654649f5f0', 'defy', 'The results defy explanation.', '这些结果令人费解。'),
  ('50627e13-92e9-4af3-b070-db654649f5f0-ex2', '50627e13-92e9-4af3-b070-db654649f5f0', 'defy', 'The operator continued to defy the injunction at peril of contempt.', '运营方继续违抗禁令，甘冒藐视法庭的风险。'),
  ('17bca94e-8bb1-4bc2-8905-315d893c25b7-ex1', '17bca94e-8bb1-4bc2-8905-315d893c25b7', 'goat', 'The goat climbed the steep rocks.', '山羊爬上了陡峭的岩石。'),
  ('17bca94e-8bb1-4bc2-8905-315d893c25b7-ex2', '17bca94e-8bb1-4bc2-8905-315d893c25b7', 'goat', 'The agency became the scapegoat, the sacrificial goat of a systemic failure.', '该机构成了替罪羊，为系统性失灵代人受过。'),
