  ('8e303ee3-d7cc-44d2-b8a1-66a41b6a05aa-ex2', '8e303ee3-d7cc-44d2-b8a1-66a41b6a05aa', 'delegate', 'The legislature may not delegate its core lawmaking function wholesale.', '立法机关不得将其核心立法职能整体委托出去。'),
  ('3075ed4e-7228-493a-b343-947bc7c9051a-ex1', '3075ed4e-7228-493a-b343-947bc7c9051a', 'delegation', 'The delegation arrived this morning.', '代表团今天上午抵达。'),
  ('3075ed4e-7228-493a-b343-947bc7c9051a-ex2', '3075ed4e-7228-493a-b343-947bc7c9051a', 'delegation', 'The doctrine limits delegation of legislative power absent intelligible principles.', '该原则限制在缺乏明确标准时委托立法权。'),
  ('0f4a1dfc-d33f-46b0-b4d1-3202f86d4990-ex1', '0f4a1dfc-d33f-46b0-b4d1-3202f86d4990', 'blessing', 'The trip was a blessing in disguise.', '这次旅行因祸得福。'),
  ('0f4a1dfc-d33f-46b0-b4d1-3202f86d4990-ex2', '0f4a1dfc-d33f-46b0-b4d1-3202f86d4990', 'blessing', 'The merger proceeded with the regulator''s qualified blessing.', '这桩合并在监管机构有保留的认可下推进。'),
  ('f3397e4e-7acf-4e33-80df-a828dabdca24-ex1', 'f3397e4e-7acf-4e33-80df-a828dabdca24', 'delete', 'Delete the old files to save space.', '删除旧文件以节省空间。'),
  ('f3397e4e-7acf-4e33-80df-a828dabdca24-ex2', 'f3397e4e-7acf-4e33-80df-a828dabdca24', 'delete', 'Spoliation rules forbid parties to delete records relevant to anticipated litigation.', '证据保全规则禁止当事人删除与预期诉讼相关的记录。'),
  ('069837c5-6805-4cb1-9277-a5bffd753ef6-ex1', '069837c5-6805-4cb1-9277-a5bffd753ef6', 'deliberate', 'She took a slow, deliberate breath.', '她缓慢而从容地吸了口气。'),
  ('069837c5-6805-4cb1-9277-a5bffd753ef6-ex2', '069837c5-6805-4cb1-9277-a5bffd753ef6', 'deliberate', 'The concealment was deliberate, sustained, and centrally directed.', '这种隐瞒是蓄意的、持续的，并由高层统一指挥。'),
  ('68d4ffe5-1524-49ca-b7b5-96e9042b8d6c-ex1', '68d4ffe5-1524-49ca-b7b5-96e9042b8d6c', 'banana', 'The monkey peeled a banana.', '猴子剥了一根香蕉。'),
  ('68d4ffe5-1524-49ca-b7b5-96e9042b8d6c-ex2', '68d4ffe5-1524-49ca-b7b5-96e9042b8d6c', 'banana', 'Banana import quotas became the flashpoint of the trade dispute.', '香蕉进口配额成了这场贸易争端的引爆点。'),
  ('f2494683-c640-42e4-afe7-01597a183f96-ex1', 'f2494683-c640-42e4-afe7-01597a183f96', 'delicious', 'The soup smells delicious.', '这汤闻起来很香。'),
  ('f2494683-c640-42e4-afe7-01597a183f96-ex2', 'f2494683-c640-42e4-afe7-01597a183f96', 'delicious', 'The irony was delicious: the auditor failed its own audit.', '这一讽刺妙不可言：审计机构没通过对自己的审计。'),
  ('5dae5c86-570e-4b14-a221-1e3d42b9e4e3-ex1', '5dae5c86-570e-4b14-a221-1e3d42b9e4e3', 'delighted', 'We are delighted to see you.', '见到你我们很高兴。'),
  ('5dae5c86-570e-4b14-a221-1e3d42b9e4e3-ex2', '5dae5c86-570e-4b14-a221-1e3d42b9e4e3', 'delighted', 'The secretariat was delighted to report full ratification by all parties.', '秘书处欣然报告所有缔约方均已完成批准。'),
  ('fb1f0ada-4403-48f1-aa41-8a0d8f429d1b-ex1', 'fb1f0ada-4403-48f1-aa41-8a0d8f429d1b', 'palace', 'The palace is open to visitors.', '宫殿对游客开放。'),
  ('fb1f0ada-4403-48f1-aa41-8a0d8f429d1b-ex2', 'fb1f0ada-4403-48f1-aa41-8a0d8f429d1b', 'palace', 'The palace''s restoration proceeded under strict heritage supervision.', '宫殿的修复在严格的遗产监管下进行。'),
  ('93f944ea-569b-4f62-8c34-ff8ee80e4630-ex1', '93f944ea-569b-4f62-8c34-ff8ee80e4630', 'demon', 'The story is about a friendly demon.', '这个故事讲的是一个友善的小恶魔。'),
  ('93f944ea-569b-4f62-8c34-ff8ee80e4630-ex2', '93f944ea-569b-4f62-8c34-ff8ee80e4630', 'demon', 'Inflation remains the demon central banks are mandated to contain.', '通胀仍是央行受命驯服的恶魔。'),
  ('ad0f200b-e141-4278-8a09-3b41ac53194d-ex1', 'ad0f200b-e141-4278-8a09-3b41ac53194d', 'formerly', 'She was formerly a teacher.', '她以前是教师。'),
