  ('6e56ae79-9cfd-4367-a663-a69d52939219-ex1', '6e56ae79-9cfd-4367-a663-a69d52939219', 'denounce', 'The group denounced the unfair rules.', '该团体谴责了不公平的规则。'),
  ('6e56ae79-9cfd-4367-a663-a69d52939219-ex2', '6e56ae79-9cfd-4367-a663-a69d52939219', 'denounce', 'Either party may denounce the treaty upon twelve months'' written notice.', '任何一方均可提前十二个月书面通知退出该条约。'),
  ('bdfc85a5-b2c7-4a64-83e2-607f9dbc8ea6-ex1', 'bdfc85a5-b2c7-4a64-83e2-607f9dbc8ea6', 'peasant', 'The peasants worked the fields at dawn.', '农民们天一亮就下地干活。'),
  ('bdfc85a5-b2c7-4a64-83e2-607f9dbc8ea6-ex2', 'bdfc85a5-b2c7-4a64-83e2-607f9dbc8ea6', 'peasant', 'The land reform redistributed estates to peasant cultivators.', '土地改革将庄园重新分配给了农民耕种者。'),
  ('2cd70b42-8b50-49f3-9ece-00d80c9909d4-ex1', '2cd70b42-8b50-49f3-9ece-00d80c9909d4', 'neat', 'Her handwriting is very neat.', '她的字迹非常工整。'),
  ('2cd70b42-8b50-49f3-9ece-00d80c9909d4-ex2', '2cd70b42-8b50-49f3-9ece-00d80c9909d4', 'neat', 'The scheme was a neat construction that collapsed under substantive scrutiny.', '这套方案构造精巧，却经不起实质审查。'),
  ('b6c028e3-efa5-435d-b909-573d80b61f35-ex1', 'b6c028e3-efa5-435d-b909-573d80b61f35', 'dentist', 'I have a dentist appointment tomorrow.', '我明天约了看牙医。'),
  ('b6c028e3-efa5-435d-b909-573d80b61f35-ex2', 'b6c028e3-efa5-435d-b909-573d80b61f35', 'dentist', 'The licensing board suspended the dentist pending the malpractice inquiry.', '在医疗事故调查期间，执业委员会暂停了这名牙医的执照。'),
