  ('7c96c937-0740-4ca4-b80e-53583e53b9a9-ex2', '7c96c937-0740-4ca4-b80e-53583e53b9a9', 'dependence', 'Dependence on a single export leaves the economy acutely vulnerable.', '对单一出口产品的依赖使该经济体极为脆弱。'),
  ('981eefeb-26a1-457d-8ad1-b2519bfa4858-ex1', '981eefeb-26a1-457d-8ad1-b2519bfa4858', 'grandparent', 'Her grandparents live nearby.', '她的祖父母住在附近。'),
  ('981eefeb-26a1-457d-8ad1-b2519bfa4858-ex2', '981eefeb-26a1-457d-8ad1-b2519bfa4858', 'grandparent', 'The statute recognizes grandparents'' standing to seek contact orders.', '该法规承认祖父母申请探视令的诉讼资格。'),
