  ('1f042f13-04af-47ae-9e85-6613e11ef245-ex2', '1f042f13-04af-47ae-9e85-6613e11ef245', 'cruise', 'The cruise operator bears liability under the passenger convention.', '根据旅客公约，邮轮运营方承担相应责任。'),
  ('cfc94301-12f8-4323-be60-66dd79a5f931-ex1', 'cfc94301-12f8-4323-be60-66dd79a5f931', 'descent', 'The plane began its descent.', '飞机开始下降。'),
  ('cfc94301-12f8-4323-be60-66dd79a5f931-ex2', 'cfc94301-12f8-4323-be60-66dd79a5f931', 'descent', 'Citizenship by descent extends to the second generation under the act.', '根据该法案，血统取得国籍延伸至第二代。'),
