  ('90480c46-74cb-4318-83ef-cd8fb7502d67-ex2', '90480c46-74cb-4318-83ef-cd8fb7502d67', 'designate', 'The minister may designate entities subject to enhanced supervision.', '部长可以指定须接受强化监管的实体。'),
  ('98bdf0e2-62cd-4594-b00a-b8daee49e7f0-ex1', '98bdf0e2-62cd-4594-b00a-b8daee49e7f0', 'mobile', 'My mobile phone needs charging.', '我的手机需要充电了。'),
  ('98bdf0e2-62cd-4594-b00a-b8daee49e7f0-ex2', '98bdf0e2-62cd-4594-b00a-b8daee49e7f0', 'mobile', 'Mobile capital migrates swiftly to the most permissive jurisdictions.', '流动资本会迅速流向监管最宽松的司法管辖区。'),
  ('2c2c5804-5710-442d-aafa-cc717f7e74a5-ex1', '2c2c5804-5710-442d-aafa-cc717f7e74a5', 'desirable', 'A quiet room is desirable for study.', '安静的房间适合学习。'),
  ('2c2c5804-5710-442d-aafa-cc717f7e74a5-ex2', '2c2c5804-5710-442d-aafa-cc717f7e74a5', 'desirable', 'Uniformity, however desirable, cannot override express statutory text.', '统一性无论多么可取，都不能凌驾于法规的明文规定之上。'),
  ('3c0f99d4-b336-41bd-8857-6aab69e9efea-ex1', '3c0f99d4-b336-41bd-8857-6aab69e9efea', 'desktop', 'The file is saved on my desktop.', '文件保存在我的电脑桌面上。'),
  ('3c0f99d4-b336-41bd-8857-6aab69e9efea-ex2', '3c0f99d4-b336-41bd-8857-6aab69e9efea', 'desktop', 'The procurement replaced every desktop across the agency''s offices.', '这次采购更换了该机构各办公室的所有台式电脑。'),
  ('49c102ca-1bec-4826-a3bd-3f3eda1be743-ex1', '49c102ca-1bec-4826-a3bd-3f3eda1be743', 'destructive', 'The storm brought destructive winds.', '暴风雨带来了破坏性大风。'),
  ('49c102ca-1bec-4826-a3bd-3f3eda1be743-ex2', '49c102ca-1bec-4826-a3bd-3f3eda1be743', 'destructive', 'The most destructive failures arose from correlated, not isolated, risks.', '最具破坏性的失灵源于关联性风险，而非孤立风险。'),
