  ('4c3095fe-94c5-4fe7-a004-5076815501b8-ex2', '4c3095fe-94c5-4fe7-a004-5076815501b8', 'diagram', 'The diagram annexed to the patent defines the claimed invention''s scope.', '专利所附图示界定了权利要求的保护范围。'),
  ('dc7d4192-5878-4b95-88a3-8143508cc811-ex1', 'dc7d4192-5878-4b95-88a3-8143508cc811', 'screening', 'The screening starts at eight.', '放映八点开始。'),
  ('dc7d4192-5878-4b95-88a3-8143508cc811-ex2', 'dc7d4192-5878-4b95-88a3-8143508cc811', 'screening', 'Investment screening extends to minority stakes in strategic sectors.', '投资审查延伸至战略行业的少数股权。'),
