  ('32901e41-870c-4235-a060-99d44a225b26-ex2', '32901e41-870c-4235-a060-99d44a225b26', 'forbid', 'The covenants forbid further borrowing absent lender consent.', '契约条款禁止未经贷款人同意的进一步举债。'),
