  ('8bc7e61b-78e4-40cc-b753-d41b24a6a51a-ex1', '8bc7e61b-78e4-40cc-b753-d41b24a6a51a', 'brutal', 'The winter here is brutal.', '这里的冬天非常严酷。'),
  ('8bc7e61b-78e4-40cc-b753-d41b24a6a51a-ex2', '8bc7e61b-78e4-40cc-b753-d41b24a6a51a', 'brutal', 'The tribunal documented brutal suppression of peaceful assembly.', '法庭记录了对和平集会的残酷镇压。'),
