  ('85936fb1-669e-4e34-9332-ff16f03223a7-ex1', '85936fb1-669e-4e34-9332-ff16f03223a7', 'disagreement', 'They had a small disagreement over dinner.', '他们吃饭时起了点小分歧。'),
  ('85936fb1-669e-4e34-9332-ff16f03223a7-ex2', '85936fb1-669e-4e34-9332-ff16f03223a7', 'disagreement', 'The panel recorded its disagreement in a sharply worded dissent.', '专家组以措辞严厉的异议意见记录了其分歧。'),
  ('9d66f5d9-0859-4e75-a525-5f26c4c6a947-ex1', '9d66f5d9-0859-4e75-a525-5f26c4c6a947', 'poke', 'Don''t poke the cake; it is still hot.', '别戳蛋糕，还烫着呢。'),
