  ('bf2e2d7a-6a0d-4037-ba2c-97ea26143dd3-ex2', 'bf2e2d7a-6a0d-4037-ba2c-97ea26143dd3', 'happily', 'Happily for the claimants, the limitation period had not yet expired.', '对索赔人来说幸运的是，诉讼时效尚未届满。'),
