  ('ba5efa23-b644-4250-bb2c-e54999a531af-ex2', 'ba5efa23-b644-4250-bb2c-e54999a531af', 'autonomy', 'The settlement preserves the region''s fiscal autonomy within defined limits.', '和解方案在限定范围内保留了该地区的财政自主权。'),
  ('5ad901b0-61aa-4ce4-bbdf-b2b7c7539e55-ex1', '5ad901b0-61aa-4ce4-bbdf-b2b7c7539e55', 'enact', 'The city enacted a new parking rule.', '该市颁布了新的停车规定。'),
  ('5ad901b0-61aa-4ce4-bbdf-b2b7c7539e55-ex2', '5ad901b0-61aa-4ce4-bbdf-b2b7c7539e55', 'enact', 'Member states must enact implementing legislation within the transposition period.', '成员国必须在转化期限内颁布实施立法。'),
  ('e6f2ba7e-c94c-42c4-b178-2c7c3e265c6a-ex1', 'e6f2ba7e-c94c-42c4-b178-2c7c3e265c6a', 'displace', 'The flood displaced hundreds of families.', '洪水使数百户家庭流离失所。'),
