  ('17f8dd3f-ddea-402a-b35c-6ac2e3497146-ex1', '17f8dd3f-ddea-402a-b35c-6ac2e3497146', 'chemistry', 'The two players have great chemistry.', '这两名球员配合默契。'),
  ('17f8dd3f-ddea-402a-b35c-6ac2e3497146-ex2', '17f8dd3f-ddea-402a-b35c-6ac2e3497146', 'chemistry', 'The chemistry of the contaminant determined the scope of remediation.', '污染物的化学性质决定了修复工作的范围。'),
  ('3c972cff-28ef-44cf-a6dd-164312802f0e-ex1', '3c972cff-28ef-44cf-a6dd-164312802f0e', 'eighteen', 'She turns eighteen next month.', '她下个月满十八岁。'),
