  ('a94f0865-293c-4453-8221-45b212855b8f-ex1', 'a94f0865-293c-4453-8221-45b212855b8f', 'rental', 'The rental car broke down.', '租来的车抛锚了。'),
  ('a94f0865-293c-4453-8221-45b212855b8f-ex2', 'a94f0865-293c-4453-8221-45b212855b8f', 'rental', 'Short-term rental platforms face registration duties under the ordinance.', '根据该条例，短租平台负有登记义务。'),
