  ('4cd50c4e-418e-4ea1-98a2-21dee63b2c79-ex2', '4cd50c4e-418e-4ea1-98a2-21dee63b2c79', 'endorsement', 'The plan secured endorsement from every class of impaired creditors.', '该方案获得了每一类受损债权人的认可。'),
  ('603c7663-ea3d-45da-bfb1-69a0e2148963-ex1', '603c7663-ea3d-45da-bfb1-69a0e2148963', 'engaged', 'They got engaged last spring.', '他们去年春天订婚了。'),
  ('603c7663-ea3d-45da-bfb1-69a0e2148963-ex2', '603c7663-ea3d-45da-bfb1-69a0e2148963', 'engaged', 'The firm was engaged in conduct the statute expressly proscribes.', '该公司从事的正是法规明文禁止的行为。'),
