  ('b8ff5498-4f29-450d-95e6-ebf48cf65175-ex1', 'b8ff5498-4f29-450d-95e6-ebf48cf65175', 'enrich', 'Reading enriches your mind.', '阅读丰富心灵。'),
  ('b8ff5498-4f29-450d-95e6-ebf48cf65175-ex2', 'b8ff5498-4f29-450d-95e6-ebf48cf65175', 'enrich', 'Officials may not exploit public office to enrich themselves.', '官员不得利用公职自肥。'),
  ('3b9d9e19-e9f6-41e3-86a2-5297bef954d6-ex1', '3b9d9e19-e9f6-41e3-86a2-5297bef954d6', 'drill', 'We had a fire drill at school today.', '今天学校举行了消防演习。'),
