  ('7473ed80-304b-4f1c-b5e2-7844721dd6bd-ex2', '7473ed80-304b-4f1c-b5e2-7844721dd6bd', 'enthusiastic', 'The market''s enthusiastic reception belied the prospectus''s buried caveats.', '市场的热烈反响掩盖了招股书中深藏的警示。'),
  ('9ad893fc-2b13-45e4-a630-de0916666496-ex1', '9ad893fc-2b13-45e4-a630-de0916666496', 'grape', 'These grapes are sweet and juicy.', '这些葡萄又甜又多汁。'),
  ('9ad893fc-2b13-45e4-a630-de0916666496-ex2', '9ad893fc-2b13-45e4-a630-de0916666496', 'grape', 'The appellation rules govern which grapes may bear the regional name.', '原产地命名规则规定哪些葡萄可以使用该地区名称。'),
