  ('4c283429-aef6-4bc9-80fa-3b956179eaaa-ex2', '4c283429-aef6-4bc9-80fa-3b956179eaaa', 'charm', 'The proposal''s charm faded once its fiscal implications were quantified.', '一旦财政影响被量化，该提案的魅力便荡然无存。'),
