  ('6bd1fb06-bdd8-4dfb-bc52-99d1419ce358-ex2', '6bd1fb06-bdd8-4dfb-bc52-99d1419ce358', 'ethic', 'The professional ethic obliges counsel to avoid conflicted representation.', '职业伦理要求律师避免存在利益冲突的代理。'),
