  ('80b6fcb5-26f2-4aac-8ec8-9c565609874a-ex1', '80b6fcb5-26f2-4aac-8ec8-9c565609874a', 'clay', 'The kids made pots out of clay.', '孩子们用黏土做陶罐。'),
