  ('ef9934f5-b9d1-46df-9a9f-2a04db098bdd-ex2', 'ef9934f5-b9d1-46df-9a9f-2a04db098bdd', 'ego', 'Institutional ego delayed the admission of error for a decade.', '机构的自负使错误的承认拖延了十年。'),
  ('8d4b6d8f-8d88-406d-805c-d30150b910d4-ex1', '8d4b6d8f-8d88-406d-805c-d30150b910d4', 'fare', 'The bus fare is two dollars.', '公交车费是两美元。'),
  ('8d4b6d8f-8d88-406d-805c-d30150b910d4-ex2', '8d4b6d8f-8d88-406d-805c-d30150b910d4', 'fare', 'Fare regulation balances operator viability against passenger affordability.', '票价监管在运营商生存与乘客承受能力之间求得平衡。'),
