  ('6e3bb92e-3f31-444e-88a3-289e60305592-ex1', '6e3bb92e-3f31-444e-88a3-289e60305592', 'homework', 'Finish your homework before dinner.', '晚饭前写完作业。'),
  ('6e3bb92e-3f31-444e-88a3-289e60305592-ex2', '6e3bb92e-3f31-444e-88a3-289e60305592', 'homework', 'The diligence failures suggest counsel simply had not done their homework.', '这些尽职调查失误表明律师根本没有做足功课。'),
