  ('79f2fd36-9653-47e2-b76b-62fc5293156c-ex1', '79f2fd36-9653-47e2-b76b-62fc5293156c', 'sofa', 'The cat curled up on the sofa.', '猫蜷在沙发上。'),
  ('79f2fd36-9653-47e2-b76b-62fc5293156c-ex2', '79f2fd36-9653-47e2-b76b-62fc5293156c', 'sofa', 'The flammability standards apply to every upholstered sofa sold domestically.', '易燃性标准适用于国内销售的所有软垫沙发。'),
