  ('3b115835-25d1-4ad4-aaf8-53a485cb5981-ex2', '3b115835-25d1-4ad4-aaf8-53a485cb5981', 'flaw', 'The methodological flaw vitiated the study''s central conclusions.', '方法论缺陷使该研究的核心结论失去效力。'),
